XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-qt4 (>= 4.6.0)
Recommends: python-hunspell
Description: QuiEdit is a distraction-free, full-screen text editor (a quiet
  editor). I initially wrote it for personal use, to write blog posts and such.
  It supports theming, basic text formatting and spell-checking. Documents are
  stored in HTML format. QuiEdit is (almost) completely controlled using
  keyboard shortcuts (type Control+H for help).

